sequenceDiagram
    participant Buyer
    participant Carrier
    participant Pikshipp
    participant LED as Ledger
    participant SW as SellerWallet
    participant FIN as Finance

    Buyer->>Carrier: pays cash on delivery
    Carrier->>Pikshipp: tracking event delivered
    Pikshipp->>LED: schedule remittance
    Pikshipp->>SW: D plus 2 credit cod_remit_to_seller
    Carrier->>Pikshipp: D plus 4 to 7 remittance file
    Pikshipp->>FIN: match by AWB
    FIN->>LED: post carrier credit
    FIN->>Pikshipp: alert on mismatches
